commit 7c7927fba98275c10ae614bd8c1a1367f87a258c
Author: Gergely Nagy <algernon@madhouse-project.org>
Date:   Thu Aug 28 12:04:32 2014 +0200

    src/ccze.c: Default to raw ANSI if stdout is not a terminal
    
    If stdout is not a terminal, use raw ANSI by default, as pagers handle
    that far better than curse. This fixes #1.
    
    Reported-by: Marcel Partap
    Signed-off-by: Gergely Nagy <algernon@madhouse-project.org>

M	src/ccze.c

commit b81e8be6f2d5f404fe9fee1adc1d1dcee652da09
Author: Gergely Nagy <algernon@madhouse-project.org>
Date:   Thu Jun 26 16:49:03 2014 +0200

    Upgrade config.* and install-sh
    
    Update the config.guess, config.sub and install-sh files from a recent
    automake. This will all go away if and when ccze is switched to
    automake.
    
    Signed-off-by: Gergely Nagy <algernon@madhouse-project.org>

M	config.guess
M	config.sub
M	install-sh

