commit 1fb3f9ec1e39b26e2831e8d1045fe38bbf76bc4e
Author: Gergely Nagy <algernon@madhouse-project.org>
Date:   Thu Jun 26 15:53:24 2014 +0200

    src/ccze-color.c: Use a static stat buffer
    
    Use a static struct stat buffer when loading a color file, so we have a
    clean starting state.
    
    Signed-off-by: Gergely Nagy <algernon@madhouse-project.org>

