commit 1de7a6e285df3aabdfd6870b6c08b0645ebd9523
Author: Gergely Nagy <algernon@madhouse-project.org>
Date:   Thu Jun 26 15:41:18 2014 +0200

    Simplify the compiler warning flags
    
    Instead of having a huge list of custom compiler warning flags, use
    -Wall -Wextra only.
    
    Signed-off-by: Gergely Nagy <algernon@madhouse-project.org>

