Date:   Thu Jun 26 15:36:33 2014 +0200

    Use 'chtype' when working with ncurses colors
    
    To silence a compile-time warning, use chtype instead of int when
    working with ncurses colors.
    
    Signed-off-by: Gergely Nagy <algernon@madhouse-project.org>

