commit ba16c0873108b73f23355f2013deb747c38d6116
Author: Gergely Nagy <algernon@bonehunter.rulez.org>
Date:   Sat Apr 26 11:48:06 2003 +0000

    Raw ANSI supports background colors
    
    * src/ccze-color.c (RAW_ANSI_BOLD): Added one more zero to the end.
      (RAW_ANSI_UNDERLINE): Likewise.
      (RAW_ANSI_REVERSE): Likewise.
      (RAW_ANSI_BLINK): Likewise.
    * src/ccze.c (ccze_addstr_internal): Added support for ANSI background
      setting, underline, reverse and blink (though they probably don't
      work :)
    
    Fixes #0000034.
    
    git-archimport-id: algernon@bonehunter.rulez.org--iluvatar-archive/ccze--0.3--patch-8

