commit c3646983a53118081ce1e9db1f3e49c8876016af
Author: Gergely Nagy <algernon@bonehunter.rulez.org>
Date:   Mon Sep 16 08:57:46 2002 +0000

    Signal colouring fix
    
    * src/ccze-wordcolor.c (ccze_wordcolor_setup): Lowercased the signal
      names in `reg_sig', since we try to apply the regexp to a lowercase
      string. Also removed the capital letters from `reg_size', for the
      same reason.
    
    git-archimport-id: algernon@bonehunter.rulez.org--iluvatar-archive/ccze--0.1--patch-36

