commit 717da61ab6ff1347d77ba8be13fc1fc9c8b51701
Author: Gergely Nagy <algernon@bonehunter.rulez.org>
Date:   Thu Sep 12 14:28:42 2002 +0000

    Initial import
    
    This is the initial import of CCZE, a clone of `colorize' written in
    C to be fast and light on resources.
    
    git-archimport-id: algernon@bonehunter.rulez.org--iluvatar-archive/ccze--0.1--base-0

